{
  "stem": "23131.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a big table, and the secretary of the-- that worked for Tovia all the time, was sitting and giving out with his orders [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] certificates that they served in the partisans from this and this date, to this and this date.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They are free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were liberated this and this date.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I consider the date [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] about July 14.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And where did you and Tovia go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed awhile there because we were very wild.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never was in Navaradok before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never-- my in-laws I never knew from before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my friends came home, like Raja.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she had a gun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had a gun.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she knew where her parents-- her parents actually were in Siberia because they transferred them there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she didn't go to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she knew where she gave away her stuff before she left for the ghetto, and she knew exactly the housing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She knew everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, you know, wild people after the woods, having a drink and all that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We went loose.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We took over the city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then, we-- Tovia had plenty of complaints that some crazy people drank too much, and they came to the-- to the-- to the Polish homes and made a lot of mischief.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the-- the mischief we didn't do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But, you know, she recognized her-- her clock on the wall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She recognized-- she recognized the-- the other things from-- from the break fronts.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she was very upset with that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she-- she wanted back and they didn't want to give her, so she threatened them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then, they went to the Pol-- to the Russian police, and they said, so, that wild people came here.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
